# GA4 API credentials for ga4-audit skill
# Provide ONE of the following (checked in order):

# Option 1: Pre-obtained access token (simplest, but expires)
# GA4_ACCESS_TOKEN=ya29...

# Option 2: Path to service account or OAuth credentials JSON file
# GA4_CREDENTIALS_PATH=/path/to/credentials.json

# Option 3: Google Application Default Credentials (standard ADC)
# GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=/path/to/service-account.json

# If none are set, the skill falls back to analytics-mcp.
